Amended Count 1 - Child Enticement - No contest plea.   Convicted.   State moves to dismiss and read in counts 2-7.   Motion granted.  Sentence is withheld.   Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for six (6) years.   Conditions of probation are:
1) Assessment/treatment/counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process;
2) Comply with sex offender registry; 
3) Have no contact wit hany minors without agent's approval;
4) Have no possession of a smart phone or internet access without agent's approval;
5) Maintain full-time employment/schooling combination; 
6) Submit DNA sample; 
7) Pay costs of action; 
8) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC; 
9) Twelve (12) months jail; Nine (9) months, up front under the Huber Law, to commence today; Three (3) months jail stayed, to be imposed upon the agent's discretion.   
Minutes.
